<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="49" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[136,1452,530,736]" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[136,201,530,556]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">Notes</emphasis>
:—Vieira (1988) recognized three subspecies for 
<taxonomicName box="[789,1010,530,556]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Campanulaceae" genus="Lobelia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="4" pageNumber="49" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="organensis">
<emphasis box="[789,1010,530,556]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">Lobelia organensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on morphological variation in trichomes, dimensions of the floral structures, and geographic distribution. Her proposal, however, could not be considered validly published, as it was part of her unpublished MSc thesis. The collection 
<emphasis box="[1186,1444,602,628]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">Prance &amp; Silva 59034</emphasis>
, assigned to the invalidly published 
<taxonomicName box="[539,909,638,664]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Campanulaceae" genus="Lobelia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="4" pageNumber="49" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="organensis" subSpecies="brasiliensis">
<emphasis box="[539,692,639,664]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">L. organensis</emphasis>
subsp. 
<emphasis box="[780,909,638,664]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">brasiliensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Vieira 1988), was later used as the 
<typeStatus box="[1329,1377,638,664]" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">type</typeStatus>
of the newly described species 
<taxonomicName box="[419,579,674,700]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Campanulaceae" genus="Lobelia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="4" pageNumber="49" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="brasiliensis">
<emphasis box="[419,579,674,700]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">L. brasiliensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Vieira, A. O. S. &amp; Shepherd, G. J." box="[595,879,674,700]" firstAuthor="Vieira" journalOrPublisher="Novon" pageId="4" pageNumber="49" pagination="457 - 460" part="8" refId="ref8361" refString="Vieira, A. O. S. &amp; Shepherd, G. J. (1998) A new species of Lobelia (Campanulaceae) from Brazil. Novon 8 (4): 457 - 460. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 3391874" title="A new species of Lobelia (Campanulaceae) from Brazil" type="journal article" year="1998">Vieira &amp; Shepherd 1998</bibRefCitation>
). The isotype cited as kept at M in the protologue was not found.
</paragraph>
